The paper deals with graph algorithms and optimization problems, which are typically categorized under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics). The problem of multiway cut is also related to computational geometry (cs.CG) and graph theory (cs.GT). Finally, the paper discusses fixed-parameter tractability and inapproximability, which are topics in computational complexity (cs.CC).
